PrecisEnactment of the ALPINE JOE SPORTSWEAR REMISSION ORDER, 1998 which provides for the remission of customs duties on fabric imported for use in the making of uniform pants or hiking pants, shorts and bicycle touring shorts, subject to specified annual limits on quantity.
